item.title: Happy Thanksgiving, Imgur!
item.description:
Thank you for all your support and comments! Here is my spread (noting that I told multiple people I wasn’t going to bother with Thanksgiving this year lol!): Turkey breast, homemade green bean casserole with my homemade cream of mushroom soup, walnut pear stuffing, mashed potatoes, my favorite turkey neck gravy, orange-pomegranate cranberries, homemade pumpkin pie with homemade crust, and my cranberry orange upside down cake!!! Hope everyone had a wonderful Thanksgiving filled with lots of food, laughter, and love! Here are the recipes I used: Gravy: https://www.triedandtruerecipe.com/how-to-the-best-turkey-gravy/ Turkey breast: https://www.triedandtruerecipe.com/how-to-roast-a-turkey-breast/ Green bean casserole: https://www.triedandtruerecipe.com/homemade-green-bean-casserole/ For my pie crust, I used this Recipe: https://www.triedandtruerecipe.com/leftover-turkey-pot-pie/ But I used the all recipes pumpkin pie filling and did NOT like it lol! I think I didn’t like the evaporated milk flavor. Upside down cake: https://www.triedandtruerecipe.com/cranberry-orange-upside-down-cake/
This was a big hit!!!
Im still proud of the pie tho - just didn’t like the evaporated milk flavor ?

“The good writing of any age has always been the product of someone's neurosis, and we'd have a mighty dull literature if all the writers that came along were a bunch of happy chuckleheads.” - William Styron I try to keep my posts "good vibe zones". So, instead of finding the one thing in here you don't like and commenting only on that, also comment about something you DID like. Balance the negativity. Love you long time. So, I made a discord server. It's a relaxed environment where you can take/donate memes to the cause, play trivia twice a week, chat about lots of topics or about nothing at all. We also have Jack Box game night and are setting up movie night! Very laid back/relaxed vibe. Come hang with us. https://discord.gg/AWFV7FT3RQ I'm also on the imgcat server for updates & fun: https://discord.gg/TpjD37jgJ9 ***Also if you miss abbiistabbii's discord community good news! Here's the new one https://discord.gg/NPStJGgARq - where everyone's reconnecting, shitposting, and hanging out again*** https://ko-fi.com/mememuseumcurator Unable to work and pretty destitute. Feel free to leave me a tip. Those that have, y'all are the bee's knees. You've helped me so much. ***Tag me if you see an artist/creator you like whose work isn't getting seen as much as it should be! Or if you are an artist/creator and want me to post something of yours, DM me! Happy Thanksgiving! I'm honestly thankful for you guys.

item.title: Oh look...
item.description:
Jim Justice and his dog. Senator Justice (R) is the one with the blue suit.
Sure... 'politically motivated'. Him and his wife owe over $13,000,000 combined in unpaid personal and business taxes.
The Greenbrier is also the site of a massive underground bunker that was meant to serve as an emergency shelter for the United States Congress during the Cold War. The bunker was code named "Project Greek Island". It became defunct a while back when it became public knowledge. Presumably there is now some other secret bunker somewhere. Jim Justice bought the resort very recently and turned it partially into a casino. Though Forbes estimates his net worth as less than zero, that might be more of a moral judgement. Funny how billionaires suddenly are broke when its time to pay taxes but then bounce back, right? The Trump Bounce.
